@startuml
title Builder - Ejemplo 6 - Builder moderno sin Director para perfil de usuario
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  class UserProfile {
    +describe(): String
    +builder(String username): Builder
  }
  class Builder {
    +displayName(String displayName): Builder
    +locale(String locale): Builder
    +enableTwoFactor(): Builder
    +disableNewsletter(): Builder
    +build(): UserProfile
  }
}

UserProfile ..> Builder : crea
Builder ..> UserProfile : crea
Main ..> UserProfile : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
